			"description": "A weapon with this trait is attached to your tail instead of held in your hands. You can only use a weapon with the tail trait if you have a tail, and you can only have one such weapon attached at any time, even if you have multiple tails. You must use an Interact action while holding a tail weapon to to attach it to your tail, and they can be Disarmed as normal."
